        <abstract> 
<p>Suggests CD have <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [6th ed.] stereotyped.</p>  
<p>Will sell out remaining copies of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> at forthcoming trade sale, print off 500 or 1000 more, and then have the type distributed.</p> 
            <p>14 copies of C. Wright’s pamphlet have been sold.</p>
